title: Bud Light Seltzer Sessions Presents: New Years Eve 2021
author: Bud Light
description: Bud Light Seltzer Sessions presents New Year's Eve 2021.  Performances by @PostMalone, @SteveAoki, @Saweetie, @SebastianYatra, @JackHarlow, hosted by @LillySingh + @MattSteffanina with @MGMResorts. Set your reminder here to tune in, or go to https://budlight.com/NYE for a more interactive viewing experience. The show starts on 12.31.20 - at 10:30 pm ET.
